        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "b236fefa07094f10",
        "text": "Platform Earth is a microservice platform for the commons. Microservices are traditionally employed by large companies, distributed across many departments and work teams, to achieve scalability, agility and the ability to maintain high reliability systems. "
      },
      "date": 1516031510181
